texts.text: >You and fellow Liberator Rika entered another world.
>Rahab, the culprit behind a slew of incidents, soon appears.
State your business with me, mortals.
We came to stop you, of course.
Please halt your invasion of our world.
Oh? And if I refuse?
We will take forceful action.
After all you've done, you've no right to complain.
So, you're here to defeat me. *Chuckle*
What simpleminded humans. So you serve the Divine now?
...! No, we don't.
The Divine are unrelated. We've come of our own volition.
And yet here you are, all the same.
This was all a part of their plan. You are but mere puppets.
No, you're twice as pathetic for thinking you have free will.
You're wrong.
R-Really?
You can't fool us, demon.
Huh? You actually believe this guy?
Please stay strong, Newbie.
We won't fall for your trivial lies, Rahab.
If you refuse to accept the truth, then words are meaningless.
I shall humor you with a fight, servants of the Divine.
So, there is no hope for compromise... How unfortunate.
Devil Download!
>Rika and [sys user_name]call upon their allies.
>The summoned demons aim straight for Rahab.
*Howl*
You asked for it!
We'll do a concentrated attack.
We'll do a pincer attack.
Understood! I'll follow your lead!
Fools.
>The two demon allies rush Rahab.
>However, his scales are impervious to both fang and sword.
...It didn't work?! That was a direct hit!
You honestly thought that would fell me?
Such puny efforts cannot hope to lay even a scratch upon me.
Tch!
Let's try again!
Let's rethink this.
Yes! The next one will strike true!
There's no time for that!
Let's devise another plan as we attack, Newbie!
It's futile. You cannot defeat me.
Die as you lament your own helplessness.
(Rahab is extremely powerful but I doubt he's invincible.)
(He must have a weak point somewhere...)
>Rika and [sys user_name]'s allies continue their fierce offensive.
>Nevertheless, the robust demon repels each attack.
>Then...
*Huff* *Huff*
What, finished already?
You won't vanquish me like that.
Ngh...
What a disappointment. I'll put you out of your misery.
>Rahab raises his massive tail.
Uh-oh, we're in big trouble! If he...
...No, it's all right. I finally understand...
Rahab is...trying to protect a certain part of his body.
Newbie... Please sync your attack with mine...
This is...our last gamble...!
Got it!
Understood!
It's useless!
I'll bet everything on this attack! Aim for...
...Beneath his chin!
>Rika and [sys user_name]'s allies dodge as they aim below Rahab's jaw.
>Then, with one all-out attack,
>They damage Rahab's scale!
*Yowl*
We...did it...
CURSES! MY BODY... HOW DARE YOU...!
YOU'LL REGRET THIS, WOMAN! I'LL CRUSH YOU TO DUST!
Uh-oh, I think that's our cue!
Let's get outta here ASAP!
>The trio escapes Rahab's fury as they vanish into thin air.
...They escaped.
Blasted woman...This isn't over.
I'll repay you for this grievous injury.
Phew, talk about a close shave.
Kokoro?! When did you...
Hey! Rika and the Newbie are all busted up!
They're unconscious! We need first aid, stat!
...Mmm. Where am I...?
Rika! Thank goodness you're awake!
Ririn? Then, this is...
Our own world. Looks like you narrowly escaped death.
I'm sure you're worn out, but can you tell us what happened?
Yes... We...
I see. So, Rahab is no pushover...
Yes, we managed to injured him once but ultimately failed.
If Kokoro hadn't saved us, then we surely would have...
Rika...
I'd say, "Don't sweat it," but that ain't your style.
"If there's life, there's hope." I learned this phrase in Japan.
Please try to think positive, Rika. You made it back alive.
You're right...
What pathetic, disappointing outcome.
...! Who're you?!
Such a clumsy escape never should have happened.
You are failed weapons who defile the Lord's name.
Another Divine?
*Sigh* It's a pain, but I'll tell you what I told the last guy.
None of this is for you.
If we're sooo unreliable, do it yourself. Don't boss us around.
What do you mean? Humans were created to serve God.
Besides, you are contractually obligated to fight in His name.
It is your most honorable duty.
This angel isn't a very good listener either.
Then how about we make ourselves crystal clear, eh?
I'll give these deaf Divine a lesson they won't soon forget.
Yay, let's do it!
Vetoed. That'll only make things worse.
Yo, Mr. Angel. I've said it once and I'll say it again.
We only fight to protect humanity.
God and his cherubs got nothin' to do with it!
Go tell your buddies to shove off!
Only fools do not delight in the Lord's work.
Nevertheless, it alters nothing. Continue to fightâ€”
As soldiers in His Army.
Hey! Wait! Clean out yer ears!
So, they dumped more on us and even had the gall to complain.

Arghhh!
I am in SUCH a bad mood right now.
That makes two of us.
Just forget all that.
Let's keep fightin' demons for the sake of mankind.
You got it.
Rika, Newbie. We'll need your help, but don't overdo it.
Understood...
